{"tid":1219332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除左Hasan Minhaj仲有好多人可以推！","createTime":"2019-06-13T19:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T04:11:20.000Z","uid":107302,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"33586ae620b1d2f4d61bd544266245db32899f85","tid":1219332,"uid":107302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:23:31.000Z","msg":"啱啱係IG見到啲人推爆左佢個comment（未去嘅即去IG @hasanminjaj comment佢最新張相），其實會關心國際新聞嘅唔只得佢一個， 仲有 @lastweektonight 嘅 John Oliver！！<br />\n<br />\n佢係2014都講過雨傘運動（傳送門：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oPun0xQsE1U），而佢之前都講過例如英國、巴西同中國嘅政治，亦都成功改變過美國政府政策（自行google:\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoPun0xQsE1U%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%BD%A2%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E9%83%BD%E8%AC%9B%E9%81%8E%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%81%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%98%85%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A6%E9%83%BD%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E9%81%8E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%EF%BC%88%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8Cgoogle%3A&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=4265b794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oPun0xQsE1U），而佢之前都講過例如英國、巴西同中國嘅政治，亦都成功改變過美國政府政策（自行google:</a> John Oliver net neutrality）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQN3jmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQN3jmK.png&h=1e8a3702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位見到嘅巴絲盡快去佢IG @lastweektonight comment，有能力嘅比埋link佢搵同搵片搵懶人包。<br />\n<br />\n我知未必有咩作用，但係呢一刻好過冇啦。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩曬各位，第一次開post唔識野，希望屌得細力啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：Last Week Tonight Instagram<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/lastweektonight?igshid=mhgt3nw8c887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Flastweektonight%3Figshid%3Dmhgt3nw8c887&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=f3e63cef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https:/